title: NZ's Synlait Milk posts a 10% jump in FY profit - Nasdaq.com
text: Sept 12 (Reuters) - New Zealand'sSynlait Milk  on Thursday posted a 10% rise in annual profit driven by higher infant formula sales during the year.
Net profit for the 12 months to July 31 came in at NZ$82.2 million ($52.72 million), up from NZ$74.6 million a year ago.
The company said full year revenue from continuing operations rose 17% to NZ$1.02 billion.
